d0b69c4ee62cb1ead274c0a2fef22fbb37bb6e","tid":539440,"uid":1613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T11:03:05.000Z","msg":"In Sam Chai,we trust <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只要你唔放棄自佢，佢唔會放棄你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"講下有咩好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T11:41:55.000Z","msg":"佢旨在幫你記少好多野，有一大堆口訣去記（咁我知好多補習都有）<br />\n另外每個topic整合既pp每題都有解釋！連mc都有，清concept一流！<br />\n最重要係佢好有心教.但喱樣野真係要感受下先知（eg佢本身主要係live班，因為overrun得太勁，video播唔哂，佢專登每一堂都錄番去比video/自選課程既同學睇得哂，跟到進度）<br />\n<br />\n明明可以請助教去幫手，佢仍然自己教哂，教到嘔血咁滯，答哂同學d問題，就係為左知同學既情況，唔識d咩，可以詳細d教.<br />\n<br />\n同埋中五中六course除左教個個topic之外仲係係topic入面搵d同之前topic有關既野，務求令你唔會唔記得哂之前d野.<br />\n<br />\n另外會講一d同topic有關既日常科學知識(eg東江水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有補過應該明）等你去鍾意讀chem!<br />\n<br />\n不過講到最後補習我講得真係人夾人，有時間的話試多幾個，所以只可以話比你知喱個老師真係好好！不妨一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6a4427529c76c78e155af76eee7f5b821aff3e","tid":539440,"uid":168158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36099179a29668944febc8a2e683c42058833e0f","tid":539440,"uid":155005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:12:18.000Z","msg":"大小型補習社都ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"用英文讀既話俾想要既topic同email我,有notes"},{"pid":"6e06319e8fa9e8aa1027671f4b81de0c2415788d","tid":539440,"uid":155005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e6a4427529c76c78e155af76eee7f5b821aff3e","tid":539440,"uid":168158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36099179a29668944febc8a2e683c42058833e0f","tid":539440,"uid":155005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:12:18.000Z","msg":"大小型補習社都ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T11:43:5